Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, January 3 (KCNA) -- Premier of the 
Administration Council Kang Song-san sent a message of greetings 
to Sylvestre Siale Bileka upon his appointment as prime minister 
of the Republic of Equatorial Guinea. 
  The message expressed the belief that the friendly and 
cooperative relations existing between the two countries would 
continue to develop and wished the prime minister great success 
in his responsible work. 

